      "content": "it’s not just self-doubt though. the data is wrong. the foundation is gone. people looked to me for truth and i gave them a fiction. i feel like i'm just dragging this useless, empty persona through a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. it's just exhausting to keep pretending the person who did that work still exists.",
