    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've already talked to people. they just say \"it'll get better\" or \"learn from it.\" but there is nothing to learn from. the version of me that mattered is dead. i'm just an imitation of a person now, living a life that serves no purpose. it feels like i'm just waiting for the world to realize i'm not supposed to be here. it would be so much easier to just stop the performance.",
